==English==

===Noun===
'''subspecific name'''
#{{zoology}} The third word in the [[scientific name]] of a [[subspecies]], following the name of the [[species]]. This applies only to formal names of animals. 
::''In the scientific name of the eastern lowland gorilla (''Gorilla beringei graueri'') the subspecific name is '''graueri''', while the subspecies name is ''Gorilla beringei graueri''. The [[specific name]] is ''beringei'' and the species name is ''Gorilla beringei''.'' 

